r. Imagine showing an American a Monty Python film to understand what Im getting at.\n\nToday I plan to have a walk around LA and a bit of a general explore before maybe heading up to Griffith Observatory in the evening to get some night time photos looking over the city. After that I have the joy of biking across one of the biggest cities in the US before making a beeline for San Diego and the Mexican border. Ive been meaning to try some surfing before heading into Mexico so I might try and find somewhere between LA and San Diego that will rent surfboards so I can embarrass myself in front of all the locals who surf constantly all year round.	Mainly plugging along the highway	usa	central-california	2023-02-18 09:56:09.027	2023-02-18 09:56:11.321	2023-02-18 09:56:11.313	1	1	2019-11-13
